database.name: Sample App Data (ORCL)
database.description: This datasource represents actual sales, booking and inventory data.

connectionPools.name: Sample Relational Connection
connectionPools.description:
Connection pool for Sample relational db source.
Instead of editing connectivity parameters in each connection pool, update the RPD and Session variables that hold that information (Manage > Variables)

You can also replace the 
"VALUEOF(NQ_SESSION.DSN)" 
by the full string below :
(DESCRIPTION=(ADDRESS_LIST=(ADDRESS=(PROTOCOL=TCP)(HOST=VALUEOF(DB_HOST))(PORT=VALUEOF(DB_PORT))))(CONNECT_DATA=(SID=VALUEOF(DB_SID))))
